      "markText": "她已撩起面纱想去吻他。她像一条经常挨打的母狗一样，露出又驯服又害怕的样子，慢慢地把身体凑过去。",
      "totalCount": 990,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=10299&rangeEnd=10346",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=10299&rangeEnd=10346"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_15_18668-18746",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "18668-18746",
      "markText": "“是的，我爱您，这是真的，很长时间来，我爱您爱得要发疯了。请不要回答我。您叫我怎么办？我已经神魂颠倒了！我爱您……唉！您要是能知道就好了，我是多么爱您啊！”",
      "totalCount": 918,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=18668&rangeEnd=18746",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=18668&rangeEnd=18746"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_15_15683-15727",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "15683-15727",
      "markText": "主持募捐的几位夫人一共收到三千多法郎，除去所有开支，净剩二百二十法郎留给第六区的孤儿们。",
      "totalCount": 900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=15683&rangeEnd=15727",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=15683&rangeEnd=15727"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_9_21866-21913",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "21866-21913",
      "markText": "他任她再三哀求，就是不答应，脸上还装出很生气的样子，后来他让步了，内心觉得这样做倒也公平合理。",
      "totalCount": 884,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=21866&rangeEnd=21913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=21866&rangeEnd=21913"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_9_13030-13083",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "13030-13083",
      "markText": "他终于弄到一个女人了，一个有夫之妇，一个上流社会的女人，真正的巴黎的上流社会的女人，来得多么容易和意外啊！",
      "totalCount": 882,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13030&rangeEnd=13083",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13030&rangeEnd=13083"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_17_7016-7057",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "7016-7057",
      "markText": "每当他听到她叫他“我的小乖乖”或“我的小宝贝”时，他就禁不住想叫她“我的老太婆”。",
      "totalCount": 858,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=7016&rangeEnd=7057",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=7016&rangeEnd=7057"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_9_34500-34557",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "34500-34557",
      "markText": "他发现这些钱的时候，骂了一句：“妈的！”顺手把钱掏出来放到背心口袋里，以便随时花用，因为他身边连一个生丁也没有了。",
      "totalCount": 852,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=34500&rangeEnd=34557",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=34500&rangeEnd=34557"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_5_2157-2183",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2157-2183",
      "markText": "他也在等待另一种东西，另一种不那么庸俗的拥抱和接吻。",
      "totalCount": 840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2157&rangeEnd=2183",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2157&rangeEnd=2183"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_10_24756-24835",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "24756-24835",
      "markText": "“为什么我们如此痛苦？无疑因为我们生下来就是要更多地依靠物质而不是依靠精神去生活，但由于我们不断思索，于是在我们日益增长的智慧和永恒不变的生活之间产生了差距。",
      "totalCount": 800,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=24756&rangeEnd=24835",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=24756&rangeEnd=24835"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_5_7049-7244",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7049-7244",
      "markText": "要人家认为你有学问并不难，总之，最重要的是不要让人当场抓住你的无知。对困难要用点手段，要避开它，遇到拦路虎就绕过去；而对别人，则要用从字典里查出来的东西难倒他。所有的人全都笨得像鹅，蠢得像鲤鱼。”",
      "totalCount": 799,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7049&rangeEnd=7244",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7049&rangeEnd=7244"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_9_32813-32891",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "32813-32891",
      "markText": "后来他突然猜出来了，他的情妇刚才不是说过一个人在穷困的时刻找到一块过去滑到衣服衬里中的金币的话吗？这是她施舍给他的金币。多丢脸的事啊！他不由得升起一股怒火。",
      "totalCount": 765,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=32813&rangeEnd=32891",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=32813&rangeEnd=32891"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_9_34147-34220",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "34147-34220",
      "markText": "开头他以为头天晚上人家不留心错把二十法郎的金路易当成一法郎找给他了，后来才恍然大悟。他的心怦怦直跳，这种接连不断的施舍简直使他感到是一种奇耻大辱。",
      "totalCount": 756,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=34147&rangeEnd=34220",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=34147&rangeEnd=34220"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_20_2735-2757",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2735-2757",
      "markText": "“因为我深深地爱着您，您明明知道，坏东西！”",
      "totalCount": 731,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2735&rangeEnd=2757",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2735&rangeEnd=2757"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "932116_21_4850-4947",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "4850-4947",
      "markText": "她看着辽阔的天际，头脑里充满诱拐的想法。她要和他走到天涯海角去！……她要被拐走！……她为此而骄傲！她一点没有想到她的名声，也不去想这件事会使她遭人唾弃。她甚至还不懂这一点，也从未想到过这一点吧？",
      "totalCount": 731,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=932116&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=4850&rangeEnd=4947",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9b532fc05e39149b5a55f66?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=4850&rangeEnd=4947"
    },
    {
